<AnchorPane xmlns="http://javafx.com/javafx/8.0.111" xmlns:fx="http://javafx.com/fxml/1" fx:controller="jc.CryptoChat.StartScene">
   <children>
      <BorderPane prefHeight="600.0" prefWidth="800.0" style="-fx-background-color: #9fe0dc;">
         <top>
            <HBox prefHeight="100.0" prefWidth="200.0" spacing="5.0" BorderPane.alignment="CENTER">
               <children>
                  <Label prefHeight="63.0" prefWidth="290.0" text="Crypto Chat">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="48.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <TextArea editable="false" prefHeight="150.0" prefWidth="443.0" text="Crypto Chat documentation:&#10;&#10;Issues worth being aware of:&#10;-Currently the program saves your keys/handle as unencrypted&#10;plain text on your harddisk right next to the program.&#10;-It only saves keys and location if you press the &quot;x&quot; button&#10;or &quot;quit&quot; if you end task it or it crashes key changes are not saved.&#10;&#10;In regards to encrpytion:&#10;-Uses One Time Pad.&#10;- Can only encrypt a-z, and spaces/commas/period (Upper case will become&#10;lower case).&#10;- Key Material uses 01010101 (binary string) key's&#10;- &quot;Your key&quot; is what you will use to encrypt, should be what they&#10;use to decrypt&#10;- &quot;Their key&quot; is what you will use to decrypt, what they should use to encrypt&#10;-Key String deleted as it is used.&#10;&#10;In regards to connecting:&#10;-You can place a hosting programs IP/Port along with extra&#10;information then press connect. Or host then give the other&#10;party your information.&#10;" />
                  <ImageView fitHeight="150.0" fitWidth="200.0" pickOnBounds="true" preserveRatio="true">
                     <image>
                        <Image url="@../../Images/splash.png" />
                     </image>
                  </ImageView>
               </children>
               <padding>
                  <Insets bottom="5.0" left="5.0" right="5.0" top="5.0" />
               </padding>
            </HBox>
         </top>
         <center>
            <GridPane BorderPane.alignment="CENTER">
              <columnConstraints>
                <ColumnConstraints hgrow="SOMETIMES" maxWidth="390.0" minWidth="10.0" prefWidth="236.0" />
                <ColumnConstraints hgrow="SOMETIMES" maxWidth="555.0" minWidth="10.0" prefWidth="554.0" />
              </columnConstraints>
              <rowConstraints>
                <RowConstraints minHeight="10.0" prefHeight="30.0" vgrow="SOMETIMES" />
                <RowConstraints minHeight="10.0" prefHeight="30.0" vgrow="SOMETIMES" />
                <RowConstraints minHeight="10.0" prefHeight="30.0" vgrow="SOMETIMES" />
                  <RowConstraints minHeight="10.0" prefHeight="30.0" vgrow="SOMETIMES" />
                  <RowConstraints minHeight="10.0" prefHeight="30.0" vgrow="SOMETIMES" />
              </rowConstraints>
               <children>
                  <Label prefHeight="63.0" prefWidth="290.0" text="IP:">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="48.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label prefHeight="63.0" prefWidth="290.0" text="Port:" GridPane.rowIndex="1">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="48.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label prefHeight="63.0" prefWidth="290.0" text="Your key:" GridPane.rowIndex="2">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="48.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label prefHeight="63.0" prefWidth="290.0" text="Their key:" GridPane.rowIndex="3">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="48.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <TextField fx:id="ip" GridPane.columnIndex="1">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="32.0" />
                     </font>
                  </TextField>
                  <TextField fx:id="port" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="1">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="32.0" />
                     </font>
                  </TextField>
                  <TextField fx:id="yourKey" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="2">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="32.0" />
                     </font>
                  </TextField>
                  <TextField fx:id="theirKey" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="3">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="32.0" />
                     </font>
                  </TextField>
                  <Label prefHeight="63.0" prefWidth="290.0" text="Handle:" GridPane.rowIndex="4">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="48.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <TextField fx:id="handle" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="4">
                     <font>
                        <Font size="32.0" />
                     </font>
                  </TextField>
               </children>
               <padding>
                  <Insets bottom="5.0" left="5.0" right="5.0" top="5.0" />
               </padding>
            </GridPane>
         </center>
         <bottom>
            <HBox prefHeight="100.0" prefWidth="200.0" spacing="15.0" BorderPane.alignment="CENTER">
               <children>
                  <Button fx:id="quit" mnemonicParsing="false" onAction="#quit" text="Quit">
